com.sap.conn.jco.ms

  • Packages that use com.sap.conn.jco.ms 
    Package Description
    com.sap.conn.jco.ms
    Contains all interfaces of JCo related to system information queries.
  • Classes in com.sap.conn.jco.ms used by com.sap.conn.jco.ms 
    Class and Description
    JCoApplicationServer
    Contains technical information about an application server of an ABAP system.
    JCoLogonGroup
    Represents a logon group of an ABAP system.
    JCoMessageServer
    The JCoMessageServer interface is the entry point for accessing the technical information of an ABAP system.
    MessageServerQueryException
    A MessageServerQueryException will be thrown, when querying the message server for information is failing.
